<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3386953>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Cratera obsidiana sp. nov.: dorsal aspect and eye pattern of fixed specimen (paratype MZU PL. 272)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3386953/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3386955>
    dc:description "FIGURES 2–8. Cratera obsidiana sp. nov., holotype in transverse (2–6) and sagittal sections with the anterior end to the left (7, 8): (2) cephalic region; (3) detail of body-margin in pre-pharyngeal region; (4) pre-pharyngeal region; (5) detail of the dorsal surface in the pre-pharyngeal region; (6) detail of the ventral surface in the pre-pharyngeal region; (7) pharynx; (8) ovary." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3386955/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3386957>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9–10. Cratera obsidiana sp. nov., composite reconstruction of the copulatory apparatus: (9) holotype in sagittal sections; (10) paratype MZU PL. 271 in horizontal sections. Anterior end to the left." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3386957/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3386959>
    dc:description "FIGURES 11–12. Cratera obsidiana sp. nov.: (11) copulatory apparatus of the holotype in sagittal section; (12) copulatory apparatus of the paratype MZU PL. 271 in horizontal section." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3386959/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

